{"tid":2387131,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連加特脫「魔」投舊主莫天才","createTime":"2021-01-30T05:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T18:04:18.000Z","uid":367552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e9efbea53ad221f42d51610dca17e075a1ac8311","tid":2387131,"uid":367552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"上季在煞科戰才開齋的曼聯中場連加特，將被外借由前帥莫耶斯領軍的韋斯咸至季尾。<br />\n曼聯中場連加特（Jesse Lingard）看來很快就能逃出奧脫福，根據《每日郵報》報道，曼聯跟韋斯咸經過一輪艱難談判後，終於達成借用協議，他將以150萬鎊費用效力韋斯咸至今季完結，對方將支付8萬鎊周薪。<br />\n<br />\n連加特近年水準急速下滑，上季全部賽事只有4球進帳，聯賽更要鬥到煞科戰對李斯特城才開齋。今季更遭蘇斯克查棄用，至今僅在盃賽上陣3次。<br />\n<br />\n現任韋斯咸領隊莫耶斯在2013/14年執教曼聯，在季前賽領軍的首個入球，就由連加特射入，不過2人合作時間不長，連加特該季先後被外借至伯明翰及白禮頓，如今將在另一球會再續前緣。<br />\n<br />\n連美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3A2QQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3A2QQY.jpg&h=5909b97e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"991c1b650ca79c670726fc63a6fed43e578bab73","tid":2387131,"uid":110878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:46:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"9b663b14f3cdec3ce259bbda2bd0398b8cd480df","tid":2387131,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T05:57:17.000Z","msg":"件垃圾踢過曼聯都光宗耀祖啦"},{"pid":"2647fb16326b8e44864becb9cbf41ba5498dd18c","tid":2387131,"uid":31208,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"連美斯 呢個名出處其實係點？"},{"pid":"bf2108702570036db6fca8f54b0aaee346933640","tid":2387131,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"2647fb16326b8e44864becb9cbf41ba5498dd18c","tid":2387131,"uid":31208,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:01:42.000Z","msg":"連美斯 呢個名出處其實係點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"Jesse lingard-&gt;messi lingard?"},{"pid":"83243773778f770270e4e13732dde32f5f7268b2","tid":238713